B.NF=new A.Q(B.a7,"Weather is critical to aviation","Weather reports and navigation documents use highly standardized vocabulary. METAR, TAF, NOTAM, and ATIS use specific terms that pilots and controllers must understand instantly.\n\nThis lesson covers the most frequently tested weather and navigation terms.",null,null,null)
